rows.name: (仮)受注条件を満たしていないときのテキスト

rows.label: qst300301_msg0001
rows.name: Aha! Just the person I wanted to see.

rows.label: qst300301_msg0002
rows.name:
When Vandham was around, all me and
Zuo had to worry about was fightin'.
But now we got details to take care of.

rows.label: qst300301_msg0003
rows.name:
We're thinking of opening a specialized
admin position for all the tedious work
that no one wants to do.

rows.label: qst300301_msg0004
rows.name:
We got three candidates, but it's a
tough call. You turned up just at the
right time, Boss.

rows.label: qst300301_msg0005
rows.name:
We need you to look 'em in the
eye and see which one's the
guy for the job.

rows.label: qst300301_msg0006
rows.name:
I know you've got an eye for people.
Your loyal compeers prove that!

rows.label: qst300301_msg0007
rows.name:
All right, I'm gonna call them up. Then
you'll need to give 'em a good grilling.
Make sure they got the right stuff.

rows.label: qst300301_msg0008
rows.name:
We'll hold the interview in the
training grounds. Give me a shout
when you're ready.
